---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout
  titulo="CI/CD转型 · 部署流水线自动化"
  descripcion="用Jenkins、GitHub Actions和质量门控替代不稳定的手动部署。实现可复现、安全的生产部署。"
>
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden" style="background-color: #0A2540;">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none opacity-40" style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(147,184,255,0.15) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 28px 28px;"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 sm:py-24">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center text-xs font-semibold px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-6" style="background: rgba(30,111,255,0.15); color: #93b8ff; border: 1px solid rgba(30,111,255,0.3);">
          CI/CD转型
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mb-5" style="letter-spacing: -0.02em;">
          告别手动部署。端到端自动化流水线。
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg max-w-2xl" style="color: rgba(147,184,255,0.8);">
          用Jenkins和GitHub Actions的全自动流水线替代脆弱的手动部署流程——集成质量门控。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CAPABILITIES -->
  <section class="bg-white py-16">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-6" style="background: #F8FAFC; border: 1px solid rgba(15,23,42,0.06);">
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold mb-2" style="color: #0A2540;">流水线审计与设计</h3>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: #64748b;">分析当前部署流程，识别瓶颈、风险和自动化机会。设计可靠的目标流水线架构。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-6" style="background: #F8FAFC; border: 1px solid rgba(15,23,42,0.06);">
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold mb-2" style="color: #0A2540;">GitHub Actions实施</h3>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: #64748b;">使用GitHub Actions构建完整CI/CD流水线——构建、测试、Docker推送和Helm部署，无需手动步骤介入。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-6" style="background: #F8FAFC; border: 1px solid rgba(15,23,42,0.06);">
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold mb-2" style="color: #0A2540;">Jenkins迁移</h3>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: #64748b;">将遗留Jenkins任务迁移至现代化的Jenkinsfile流水线即代码。并行阶段、共享库和声明式语法提升可维护性。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-6" style="background: #F8FAFC; border: 1px solid rgba(15,23,42,0.06);">
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold mb-2" style="color: #0A2540;">质量门控与测试</h3>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: #64748b;">集成SonarCloud进行自动代码质量分析。覆盖率阈值和安全扫描可靠地阻断低质量代码的部署。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-6" style="background: #F8FAFC; border: 1px solid rgba(15,23,42,0.06);">
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold mb-2" style="color: #0A2540;">部署验证</h3>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: #64748b;">每次部署后自动执行健康检查和冒烟测试。检查失败时自动触发回滚机制——无需人工干预。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-6" style="background: #F8FAFC; border: 1px solid rgba(15,23,42,0.06);">
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold mb-2" style="color: #0A2540;">指标与可见性</h3>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: #64748b;">将部署频率、前置时间、MTTR作为可量化指标追踪。仪表盘展示CI/CD转型随时间推移的进展。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section style="background: #0A2540;" class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">转型您的部署流程。</h2>
      <p class="text-base mb-8" style="color: rgba(147,184,255,0.8);">从流水线审计开始，提供完整CI/CD自动化的具体实施计划。</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-3.5 rounded-xl font-semibold text-white" style="background: #1E6FFF;">
        联系我们
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
